    <h2>
        About</h2>
    <p>
        The Tampa Bay Area ASP.NET MVC Developer Group is a monthly developer group in Tampa,
        Florida focusing on building skill and confidence at developing web applications
        using the ASP.NET MVC Framework. Meetings consist of presentations by experts, code
        reviews of popular MVC architectures and applications, and lightning talks by members
        on specific MVC topics. During the course of the year presentations and code samples
        get more specific and challenging to increase the development skills of its members.
    </p>
